<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Verification</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Account Verification</h1>
  <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
  <p>Thank you for registering! Please use the following OTP to verify your account:</p>
  <h2>{{otp}}</h2>
  <p>This OTP is valid for a short period, so please use it promptly.</p>
  <p>If you did not attempt to create an account, please ignore this email.</p>
  <p>Thank you,</p>
  <p>Telytech Team</p>
</body>
</html>